  "title": "Accounts Executive (Navision)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Handle full sets of accounts including AP, AR, GL, bank reconciliations, and month-end/year-end closing.</li><li>Prepare financial schedules, management reports, and support audit and tax submissions.</li><li>Ensure accurate records and compliance with accounting standards and internal controls.</li><li>Perform daily accounting operations using <strong>Navision (Microsoft Dynamics NAV).</strong></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Accountancy or equivalent.</li><li>At least 2 years of experience in handling <strong>full sets of accounts.</strong></li><li>Proficient with <strong>Navision system.</strong></li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
